messages.message:
Hey, debugged further. Looks like this is related to M1 systems. Tried to run it on intel machine and works fine.
This has happened after recent package + base image upgrade.
For now to unblock, we can run `ocr-service` by setting `"enable_ocr_ari": false` as we don't use ari ocr-engine under `data-services/ocr-services/ocr-service/deployment/env/deployment-config.json` and `shared-utils/build-utils/shared/env-local.json`
